#: templates/about.html:3
msgid "Le Jeu Des Images - A propos"
msgstr "The Image Game - About"

#: templates/about.html:6
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Decouvrez l'histoire et l'equipe derriere Le Jeu Des Images, un jeu "
"interactif pour identifier les membres de l'equipe %(company_name)s."
msgstr ""
"Discover the story and team behind The Image Game, an interactive game to"
" identify %(company_name)s team members."

#: templates/about.html:9 templates/base_page.html:54
msgid "A propos"
msgstr "About"

#: templates/about.html:10
msgid "Decouvrez l'histoire et l'equipe derriere Le Jeu Des Images"
msgstr "Discover the story and team behind The Image Game"

#: templates/about.html:14
msgid "Notre histoire"
msgstr "Our story"

#: templates/about.html:16
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Le Jeu Des Images est ne d'une volonte de creer un outil ludique et "
"interactif pour aider les nouveaux collaborateurs a se familiariser avec "
"les membres de l'equipe %(company_name)s."
msgstr ""
"The Image Game was born from a desire to create a fun and interactive "
"tool to help new employees get to know the %(company_name)s team members."

#: templates/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Ce projet a ete developpe avec passion pour favoriser l'integration et "
"renforcer la cohesion d'equipe au sein de notre entreprise."
msgstr ""
"This project was developed with passion to foster onboarding and "
"strengthen team cohesion within our company."

#: templates/about.html:22
msgid "Notre mission"
msgstr "Our mission"

#: templates/about.html:24
msgid ""
"Notre mission est de faciliter l'apprentissage des visages et des noms de"
" vos collegues de maniere amusante et engageante."
msgstr ""
"Our mission is to make learning your colleagues' faces and names fun and "
"engaging."

#: templates/about.html:25
msgid ""
"Grace a differents modes de jeu, vous pouvez tester et ameliorer votre "
"connaissance de l'equipe tout en vous amusant."
msgstr ""
"Through different game modes, you can test and improve your knowledge of "
"the team while having fun."

#: templates/about.html:30
msgid "L'equipe de developpement"
msgstr "The development team"

#: templates/about.html:32
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Le Jeu Des Images a ete concu et developpe par une equipe passionnee de "
"developpeurs et de designers de %(company_name)s."
msgstr ""
"The Image Game was designed and developed by a passionate team of "
"developers and designers from %(company_name)s."

#: templates/about.html:33
msgid ""
"Nous travaillons constamment a ameliorer l'experience utilisateur et a "
"ajouter de nouveaux modes de jeu pour rendre l'apprentissage encore plus "
"amusant."
msgstr ""
"We are constantly working to improve the user experience and add new game"
" modes to make learning even more fun."

#: templates/about.html:38
msgid "Contactez-nous"
msgstr "Contact us"

#: templates/about.html:40
msgid ""
"Vous avez des suggestions ou des commentaires pour ameliorer Le Jeu Des "
"Images ? N'hesitez pas a nous contacter !"
msgstr ""
"Have suggestions or feedback to improve The Image Game? Feel free to "
"reach out!"

#: templates/about.html:41
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Envoyez-nous un email a %(email_link)s ou parlez-en directement a un "
"membre de l'equipe de developpement."
msgstr ""
"Send us an email at %(email_link)s or speak directly with a member of the"
" development team."

