#: templates/how_to_play.html:3
msgid "Le Jeu Des Images - Comment jouer"
msgstr "The Image Game - How to play"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:6
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Apprenez a jouer au Jeu Des Images et decouvrez les regles des differents"
" modes de jeu pour identifier les membres de l'equipe %(company_name)s."
msgstr ""
"Learn how to play The Image Game and discover the rules of the different "
"game modes to identify %(company_name)s team members."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:10
msgid "Decouvrez les regles et astuces pour maitriser tous les modes de jeu"
msgstr "Discover the rules and tips to master all game modes"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:14
msgid "Principes de base"
msgstr "Basic principles"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:16
msgid ""
"Le Jeu Des Images est concu pour vous aider a memoriser les visages et "
"les noms de vos collegues de maniere ludique et interactive."
msgstr ""
"The Image Game is designed to help you memorize your colleagues' faces "
"and names in a fun and interactive way."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:17
msgid ""
"Chaque mode de jeu propose un defi different, mais l'objectif reste le "
"meme : associer correctement les visages aux noms, equipes et postes."
msgstr ""
"Each game mode offers a different challenge, but the goal remains the "
"same: correctly match faces with names, teams and positions."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:22 templates/mode_selection.html:18
msgid "Modes de jeu classiques"
msgstr "Classic game modes"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:24 templates/scores.html:21
msgid "Mode Normal"
msgstr "Normal Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:25
msgid ""
"Dans ce mode, vous voyez la photo d'un collaborateur et devez identifier "
"son entreprise, son equipe, son nom et son poste. Vous gagnez des points "
"pour chaque bonne reponse."
msgstr ""
"In this mode, you see a colleague's photo and must identify their "
"company, team, name and position. You earn points for each correct "
"answer."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:27 templates/scores.html:41
msgid "Mode Inverse"
msgstr "Reverse Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:28
msgid ""
"A l'inverse du mode normal, vous voyez un nom et devez identifier la "
"personne parmi plusieurs photos. Ce mode teste votre memoire visuelle."
msgstr ""
"Unlike normal mode, you see a name and must identify the person among "
"several photos. This mode tests your visual memory."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:30 templates/scores.html:61
msgid "Mode Pixelation"
msgstr "Pixelation Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:31
msgid ""
"L'image d'un collaborateur apparait progressivement, devenant de plus en "
"plus nette. Plus vite vous identifiez la personne, plus vous gagnez de "
"points."
msgstr ""
"A colleague's image appears progressively, becoming clearer and clearer. "
"The faster you identify the person, the more points you earn."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:33 templates/scores.html:81
msgid "Mode Chronometre"
msgstr "Timed Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:34
msgid ""
"Similaire au mode normal, mais avec une limite de temps pour repondre. La"
" pression est a son comble !"
msgstr ""
"Similar to normal mode, but with a time limit to answer. The pressure is "
"on!"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:39 templates/mode_selection.html:119
msgid "Modes de jeu experimentaux"
msgstr "Experimental game modes"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:41
msgid ""
"Decouvrez nos modes de jeu experimentaux pour des defis encore plus "
"varies :"
msgstr "Discover our experimental game modes for even more varied challenges:"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:43
msgid "Mode Memoire"
msgstr "Memory Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:43
msgid "Retrouvez les paires correspondantes, comme dans un jeu de memory."
msgstr "Find matching pairs, like in a memory card game."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:44
msgid "Mode Equipe"
msgstr "Team Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:44
msgid "Identifiez les membres d'une equipe specifique."
msgstr "Identify the members of a specific team."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:45
msgid "Mode Indice"
msgstr "Clue Mode"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:45
msgid "Utilisez des indices pour identifier la personne."
msgstr "Use clues to identify the person."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:46
msgid "Et bien d'autres"
msgstr "And many more"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:46
msgid "a decouvrir par vous-meme !"
msgstr "to discover for yourself!"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:52
msgid "Astuces pour progresser"
msgstr "Tips to improve"

#: templates/how_to_play.html:55
msgid ""
"Commencez par le mode normal pour vous familiariser avec les visages et "
"les noms."
msgstr "Start with normal mode to get familiar with the faces and names."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:56
msgid ""
"Utilisez le mode pixelation pour tester votre capacite a reconnaitre "
"rapidement vos collegues."
msgstr ""
"Use pixelation mode to test your ability to quickly recognize your "
"colleagues."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:57
msgid "Jouez regulierement pour ameliorer votre memoire des visages et des noms."
msgstr "Play regularly to improve your memory of faces and names."

#: templates/how_to_play.html:58
msgid ""
"N'hesitez pas a explorer tous les modes de jeu pour une experience "
"complete."
msgstr "Feel free to explore all game modes for a complete experience."

